to\": 1630}, {\"ngram\": \"the sport\", \"from\": 1642, \"to\": 1651}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The diminutive all-time 1,500-metre great grew up in western Kenya's Rift Valley, which is renowned as a breeding ground for runners.\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1787, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1715, \"end\": 1720, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.999999787770116, \"rank\": 1.4841149160312105e-07, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The diminutive all-time 1,500-metre great\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1695}, {\"ngram\": \"a breeding ground\", \"from\": 1757, \"to\": 1774}, {\"ngram\": \"runners\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1786}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The world record holder's journey began in the ever-changing muddy, dusty and hilly terrain of Ndababit village, 233km (144 miles) west of Kenya's capital Nairobi.\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1928, \"end\": 1933, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.999999787770116, \"rank\": 1.4841149160312105e-07, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 1944, \"end\": 1951, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\", \"score\": 0.9999999901133378, \"rank\": 9.840156993700768e-09, \"text\": \"Nairobi\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Nairobi\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The world record holder's journey\", \"from\": 1789, \"to\": 1822}, {\"ngram\": \"the ever-changing muddy, dusty and hilly terrain\", \"from\": 1832, \"to\": 1880}, {\"ngram\": \"Ndababit village\", \"from\": 1884, \"to\": 1900}, {\"ngram\": \"233km\", \"from\": 1902, \"to\": 1907}, {\"ngram\": \"144 miles\", \"from\": 1909, \"to\": 1918}, {\"ngram\": \"west\", \"from\": 1920, \"to\": 1924}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I used to run barefoot from my village to the primary school because in Kenya, schools are so far that you always end up running in order to reach them in time,\\\" Kipyegon told Al Jazeera before theDiamond League event in Doha.\", \"from\": 1954, \"to\": 2181, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2027, \"end\": 2032, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"score\": 0.999999787770116, \"rank\": 1.4841149160312105e-07, \"text\": \"Kenya\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kenya\"}, {\"begin\": 2131, \"end\": 2141, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"score\": 0.9780384713556618, \"rank\": 0.022454019005893056, \"text\": \"Al Jazeera\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\", \"Q15265344\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Al_Jazeera\"}, {\"begin\": 2176, \"end\": 2180, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"score\": 0.9509993205489049, \"rank\": 0.051525462103182214, \"text\": \"Doha\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Doha\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my village\", \"from\": 1983, \"to\": 1993}, {\"ngram\": \"the primary school\", \"from\": 1997, \"to\": 2015}, {\"ngram\": \"schools\", \"from\": 2034, \"to\": 2041}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 2087, \"to\": 2092}, {\"ngram\": \"time\", \"from\": 2110, \"to\": 2114}, {\"ngram\": \"Kipyegon\", \"from\": 2117, \"to\": 2125}, {\"ngram\": \"theDiamond League event\", \"from\": 2149, \"to\": 2172}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I have loved [running] since I was a little girl, but I never thought I would become an Olympic champion one day,\\\" she said with a chuckle.\", \"from\": 2183, \"to\": 2323, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"