gram\": \"a competitive comeback\", \"from\": 2604, \"to\": 2626}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"It was not easy as I could barely walk 20 minutes the first time I stepped back on the track,\\\" she said in a social media video in 2022, as she reflected on the difficulties of returning to the track after having given birth.\", \"from\": 2629, \"to\": 2855, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2713, \"to\": 2722}, {\"ngram\": \"a social media video\", \"from\": 2737, \"to\": 2757}, {\"ngram\": \"the difficulties\", \"from\": 2787, \"to\": 2803}, {\"ngram\": \"the track\", \"from\": 2820, \"to\": 2829}, {\"ngram\": \"birth\", \"from\": 2849, \"to\": 2854}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"But the strength Alyn gives me has helped me overcome all challenges.\\\"\", \"from\": 2857, \"to\": 2928, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2875, \"end\": 2879, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Alyn\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Alyn\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Alyn\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/River_Alyn\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the strength\", \"from\": 2862, \"to\": 2874}, {\"ngram\": \"all challenges\", \"from\": 2912, \"to\": 2926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English:\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2974, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Follow Al Jazeera English\", \"from\": 2948, \"to\": 2973}]}]}"